name: WackD'Quack
description:
WackD'Quack is Here !!!.

It is A Casual 2d Fun tapping Addictive  game where you have to Wack the Ducks and Fish to get higher score ,your main aim is not only to hunt the ducks but to stop them from escaping,the game is infinite based along with vast variety of stages of every season
